Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:29.59,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:36.89,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:44.39,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:48.23,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:54.45,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:58.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.58,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:10.25,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.46,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:17.22,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:28.40,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There was a fire early this\Nmorning at the private residence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}of Diet member Tabata Shigeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:44.00,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\be8\an7\pos(162,745.5)\fscx60\b1}Diet member Tabata killed\N\N{\fscx98\fs108\bord7.5\be8}Was smoking in bed the cause?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The fire burned the\Nbedroom and part of the hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}before it was put out, but what\Nseems to be the body of Mr. Tabata
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}was discovered within the ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a terrible shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had been looking forward to having Tabata
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,work even harder with us in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There is strong suspicion\Nthat smoking in bed was the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he a regular smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard that he was a heavy smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is too bad, in any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister, the esteemed Toki is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, send him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good work last night.\NCome, take a seat! Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it has been too long\Nsince we've had breakfast together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Special ability research?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is some pretty\Nnasty stuff you're up to, "{\i1}Souri.{\i}"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.46,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"souri: 'Prime Minister'"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the "{\i1}Souri,{\i}" it's troubling\Nfor you to "{\i1}so re{\i0}-fer" to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Sorry.{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, if I could take some of the burden
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,off of you Code: Breakers, even a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm placing hardship upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As your father, I am\Nconscious of that above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do something\Neven the least bit fatherly, and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Code: Breaker.\NYou are not my father, nor am I your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still upset about Nenene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains my heart, as well,\Nto have put her in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised. I would become\Nyour dog, and wipe out evil men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We would lay off Sissy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we decided, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard. Apparently, you quietly\Nwent to see her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Nenene doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miserable coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\be6\an8}"Episode 6: 'Lost One'"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.89,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Diet member Tabata dead"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what government power can do, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The government controls the Code: Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows, do they?\NEven with all that was being done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a favor from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you give us a little space?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden is not happy about you\Nbringing Sakurakoji Sakura
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,into Tabata's residence,\Nand exposing her to danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden is concerned with Miss Sakurakoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders from Eden...\Nyou are to be her escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me? I want Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me the song and dance!\NJust work hard and smart! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're not a big fan of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I don't like them, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you cop such a flagrant attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it just makes it harder to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a look into the girl myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a rarebreed notwithstanding,\Nthere must be some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,why they're putting a\NCode: Breaker on her as a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working too much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to go Lost, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty woman.\NIs she a Code: Breaker, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Toki, and that woman just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, you've got quite\Na few friends, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have friends. I'm a\NCode: Breaker, who doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. I am relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important that you\Nhave people that care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're here anyway,\Nyou should become friends
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with everyone in the class, and not\Njust your Code: Breaker pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be more fun that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Were I to become friends with my classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they could still not contribute\Nanything toward my objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of time. It would\Nbe foolish to get overly involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and let them become aware of who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the Code: Breakers are not my pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just colleagues,\Nwho have a common interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A good morning to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? N-Nothing at all! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Nothing, nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.77,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Fire at Diet Member Tabata's Estate"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't mess up my desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time for class to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass these handouts around.\NYou've got thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakurakoji, no looking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right! My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows, do they?\NEven with all that was being done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell my secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will burn up your friends\Nwithout a second thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"In the dark, the young man held\Nhis breath, concealing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Harboring his doubts, the young man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,stole his way into the\Nattic over the woman's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,eager to ascertain the truth for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.72,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"The Schoolmistress"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak... Squeak...\NThe floor in the woman's room creaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man peered into the\Nroom through a small gap in the planks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man saw her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the woman, stretched out upon the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, with a rough rope in hand,\Nas she approached the woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the schoolmistress smiled\Nbeguilingly, and said..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Would you please stop reading\Nsmutty novels aloud
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,here in the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not smutty.\NIt is a work of art by Kanno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're reading it too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was unable to contain the\Noverflowing adoration
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have for such artistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, you are within sight of the Dead Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji, I'd like to go\Nin the classroom to get my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not enter right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm doing something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a shock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm super-surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make sure no one finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji, is that about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami is outside! Everyone, shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait, Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami! Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you sneaking around about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.63,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ogami Rei"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:56.55,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Welcome to Class 1-B!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, welcome to Class 1-B!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry your welcome party is so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus it's as late as it is,\Nonce our club activities are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still make it to your job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! The guest of honor gets to wear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We all got this ready for you,\Nbut we rushed, so it's not too pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Ogami. Your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:30.29,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Takeshi Aoki"\N"Let's go to the arcade across from the\Nstation! I heard you once lived in Tokyo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn all our names, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? We're gonna be\Nin class together a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Best that we enjoy it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Ogami, you're always smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but you seem to have trouble\Ntalking to anyone but Sakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so we thought that maybe you\Nwere forcing yourself to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept our regards, Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Regards!\N- Regards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just found out myself this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked me to keep\Nyou out of the classroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so they could get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitta... Yagi... Yusa... Watanabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They all care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a little bit friendly\Nback to them wouldn't go amiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After all they did for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I dislike things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When a person dies,\Ntheir things are left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take care of mine ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aoki Takeshi... Let's go to the arcade."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aoyama Yukio... My hobby is mountain climbing."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ijuin Hikari... Blond Love."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Uesugi Hajime... Please teach me some English."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've memorized all the data written on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, knowing that group,\Nthey'd pester me if I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a non-existent being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't need any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...? Good grief, you! You're so defiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... This soon? Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The report from Agent Kamura\Nthat said he had located the target
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was cut off at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That now makes forty-three\Nagents who have gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This former Code: Breaker,\NHitomi, is quite the piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Every bit the Code 01, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I wonder how they will strike this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning, Yukihina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten quite a few of them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to use them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Ogami was pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He never really is very expressive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that true. I wonder how\Nhe and Sakura are getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I intentionally left them alone with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so if they're not getting along,\NI'll be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so the two of them are on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose that right at this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right at this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami! If you don't make Miss Sakurakoji happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Ogami, now that\Nyou've learned everyone's names,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the end of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go clean up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, now! What do you... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just come\Nin here without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Ogami! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! These guys are already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These corpses are just being controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who could do this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, taking measures was the right idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miss Kanda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... Hitomi's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you later. We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Inside the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! We must get everyone to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanda! Keep Miss Sakurakoji protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will burn up anyone who crosses these flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A tooth for a tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil for evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, are you sure that what\Nyou really value more than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Number six! I'm coming... to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu... ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine, getting yourself this pinned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Points off for that, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for you, Yuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's nice that you're on time,\Nbut your work is sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already within the Dead Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye; a tooth for a tooth;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,eternal rest... for the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The light special ability is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Heike is a Code: Breaker, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami! Ogami, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the destiny of us Code: Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is our unavoidable... fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:22:01.55,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:07.22,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:21.73,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:27.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.91,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:37.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:42.34,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:46.34,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:51.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:55.85,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:00.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:05.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:13.74,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it is an unavoidable fate,\NI cannot accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time,\N"Code: Breaker" episode 7,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sakura, In the Light."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami! Ogami!
